data.description: Well maintained 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home situated on a large fenced yard. Home offers a spacious kitchen with abundant amount of cabinet space. Living room with built in shelving, patio door leading out to a large deck. Newer gas furnace with central air, new hot water heater, attached garage with workshop, updated bathroom with tile surround, large foyer, lower level master bedroom with large closet. This home is within walking distance of anything you could need: groceries, gas, entertainment, parks, schools and more!
